Usage: MEMO [memo text] 
   The first form of the command, will save any text included to a file,
   which can be retrived using the second form of the command (no
   arguments specified)

   The memo file will be saved in the help directory for access with
   the internal viewer.

ie.
    /MEMO this is a test.
    Then the memo's can be viewed with
    /MEMO

See also: [DUMP]

